                    <p>A Mumbai business on Xero files GSTR-3B on the 22nd and reconciles the bank feed monthly. The audit-trail export has to be ready when the auditor asks. Maharashtra profession tax (PTRC) is also due by the 15th each month. For xero bookkeeping in Mumbai, Patron keeps every date on schedule; book a review on +91 94594 56700 or see our <a href="/blog/cost-of-accounting-services-mumbai-2026">local notes</a>.</p>

